Text translation system by SMS using Textlocal

edit the index.php page, entering your username and password

Set your Textlocal inbound system to send messages to the index.php file here.

Send a message starting with the language (eg ES for spanish) plus the message, and a response gets sent with the translated text.

NOTE: You will also need to register for an API key from the Microsoft website:

http://www.microsoft.com/web/post/using-the-free-bing-translation-apis
